style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>2. Real-Time Chat
&amp; Communications<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p>The mobile app also provides a robust interface for synchronous messaging to
ensure teams stay connected away from their desks.</p>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Deep Dive: Core
Functions &amp; Capabilities<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Instant Messaging</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Seamless integration
     with the web platform's chat infrastructure. Direct Messages (DMs) and
     Channel messages sync instantly via <span class=SpellE>WebSockets</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Presence Indicators</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Users can view the
     online/offline status of colleagues directly from the mobile directory.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l6 level1 lfo4;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Push Notifications</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Real-time push alerts
     for </span><code><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>@mentions</span></code><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'> and direct messages
     ensure critical communications are never missed.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>End-to-End User
Workflow<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Triaging Messages</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: The user opens the
     Chat tab to view a chronologically sorted list of recent conversations,
     with bold indicators for unread threads.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l3 level1 lfo5;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Responding</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: The user taps a
     thread, reads the history, and uses the native keyboard to quickly send a
     response, complete with emoji support.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>

<hr size=2 width="100%" align=center>

</span></div>

<h2><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id="Picture_x0020_2"
 o:spid="_x0000_i1056" type="#_x0000_t75" style='width:282pt;height:626.4pt;
 visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>
 <v:imagedata src="Forge_Connect_Mobile_Manual_files/image003.jpg" o:title=""/>
</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=376 height=835
src="Forge_Connect_Mobile_Manual_files/image004.jpg" v:shapes="Picture_x0020_2"><![endif]></span><span
style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></h2>

<h2><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>3. Mail, Docs,
Sheets &amp; Show<o:p></o:p></span></h2>

<p>To ensure full feature parity with the web platform, the mobile application
provides dedicated tabs for accessing the core workspace productivity apps.<o:p></o:p></p>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Deep Dive: Core
Functions &amp; Capabilities<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ul type=disc>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Web-to-Mobile Continuity</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: The Mail, Docs,
     Sheets, and Show applications are integrated into the mobile shell via
     responsive, touch-friendly interfaces, providing a seamless transition
     from desktop to mobile.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Mail App</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: View your inbox, read
     secure enterprise emails, and compose messages on the go with responsive
     reading panes. With AI Integrated we can generate Mails Quickly<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Docs &amp; Sheets App</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: View and
     collaboratively edit Rich-Text documents and Data Grids in real-time. The
     UI adapts to touch controls for selecting cells and formatting text.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Show App</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Review presentations
     and slide decks directly from your mobile device before heading into a
     meeting.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l7 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Unified Navigation</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: Users can seamlessly
     tab between active meetings, chat channels, and their documents without
     losing state.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ul>

<h3><span style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>End-to-End User
Workflow<o:p></o:p></span></h3>

<ol start=1 type=1>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Quick Document Review</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: While commuting, a
     user taps the &quot;Docs&quot; tab, navigates to the &quot;Q3
     Campaign&quot; folder, and reviews the latest changes made by their team.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Checking Spreadsheets</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: The user opens the
     &quot;Sheets&quot; tab to quickly verify a financial figure in the active
     workspace spreadsheet, ensuring they have the correct data before an
     ad-hoc video call.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
 <li class=MsoNormal style='mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;
     mso-list:l1 level1 lfo8;tab-stops:list 36.0pt'><strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>Reading Mail</span></strong><span
     style='mso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman"'>: The user triages new
     messages from the &quot;Mail&quot; tab, marking important items for
     follow-up later on their desktop.<o:p></o:p></span></li>
</ol>

